to a phone, to a computer,

00:06:18.270 --> 00:06:21.517
to a billboard, to
in-store signage-- what

00:06:21.517 --> 00:06:23.850
do you think really has the
most influence on purchasing

00:06:23.850 --> 00:06:24.350
decisions?

00:06:27.080 --> 00:06:27.579
Steven.

00:06:27.579 --> 00:06:29.050
