becoming more like tablets.

00:06:47.230 --> 00:06:49.690
So the line is getting blurred.

00:06:49.690 --> 00:06:50.690
LISA GREEN: The phablet?

00:06:50.690 --> 00:06:51.440
STEVEN ALAN: Yeah.

00:06:51.440 --> 00:06:52.522
I guess.

00:06:52.522 --> 00:06:54.590
LISA GREEN: Anything
else you guys think?

00:06:54.590 --> 00:06:57.825
