and tablet are becoming so big?

00:06:57.825 --> 00:06:58.700
LAUREN SHERMAN: Yeah.

00:06:58.700 --> 00:07:00.770
Obviously I agree
that mobile is huge.

00:07:00.770 --> 00:07:04.590
