00:07:51.050 --> 00:07:54.350
mobile kind of connects
you while you're in store.

00:07:54.350 --> 00:07:56.620
If you could sort
of create-- Steven,

00:07:56.620 --> 00:07:58.080
maybe for you in your stores?

00:07:58.080 --> 00:08:00.910
How do you feel like your--
you guys should be using mobile

00:08:00.910 --> 00:08:02.259
