the store and then,

00:08:08.270 --> 00:08:10.890
if we don't have something,
then usually the associate

00:08:10.890 --> 00:08:13.870
will go online and see
if we have it online.

00:08:13.870 --> 00:08:16.360
Then they'll be able to
help them and complete

00:08:16.360 --> 00:08:17.460
that purchase online.

00:08:17.460 --> 00:08:20.010
Or, if another store
has it, again they

00:08:20.010 --> 00:08:26.047
can check inventory with the
same app at and other stores,

00:08:26.047 --> 00:08:26.630
and sell that.

00:08:26.630 --> 00:08:26.840
Had

00:08:26.840 --> 00:08:27.950
LAUREN SHERMAN: Yeah,
it's such a simple thing.

00:08:27.950 --> 00:08:30.430
But my husband's a big
fan of Steven's stuff.

00:08:30.430 --> 00:08:33.690
And he-- that, like,
sea-green sweatshirt you guys

00:08:33.690 --> 00:08:34.460
did for spring?

00:08:34.460 --> 00:08:35.520
He really wanted it.

