available in the Tribeca store.

00:08:40.970 --> 00:08:41.909
So he went there.

00:08:41.909 --> 00:08:44.075
That's something that's
been around for a long time.

00:08:44.075 --> 00:08:46.202
But I feel like people
are really using it now.

00:08:46.202 --> 00:08:48.660
Whereas maybe five years ago,
he wouldn't have even thought

00:08:48.660 --> 00:08:51.481
of checking to see if it
was available in a store,

00:08:51.481 --> 00:08:53.480
or he would have picked
up the phone and called,

