00:09:05.320 --> 00:09:06.470
But we have it.

00:09:06.470 --> 00:09:08.460
And it would be by the SKU.

00:09:08.460 --> 00:09:11.390
So it won't tell you to call
a store if they don't actually

00:09:11.390 --> 00:09:14.260
have that size in that item.

00:09:14.260 --> 00:09:17.750
But then, 2.0 would
definitely be--

00:09:17.750 --> 00:09:20.910
online would actually just
start scanning all the stores.

00:09:20.910 --> 00:09:26.250
